== 發行 ==
《落日殺神》在北美由夢工廠發行，排定2004年8月6日上映，[[派拉蒙影業|派拉蒙影業]]則負責國際市場發行和影碟銷售<ref name="Filmaffinity" /><ref name="HDReport(2020-09-28)">{{cite news|url=https://hd-report.com/2020/09/28/collateral-2004-upgraded-to-4k-ultra-hd-blu-ray/|title=Collateral (2004) upgraded to 4k Ultra HD Blu-ray|work=HD Report|date=2020-09-28|accessdate=2021-07-13|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120120614/https://hd-report.com/2020/09/28/collateral-2004-upgraded-to-4k-ultra-hd-blu-ray/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2004年8月4日，電影被選為第8屆都市世界影展（{{lang|en|Urbanworld Film Festival}}）的開幕影片，主演和電影人均出席這場位於紐約市{{le|魔術強森戲院|Magic Johnson Theatres}}活動<ref name="BusinessWire(2004-06-18)" />。9月3日登上[[第61屆威尼斯影展|第61屆威尼斯影展]]，以非競賽片身份放映<ref name="LaBiennale-1">{{cite web|url=http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/61miac/line-up/out-of-competition.html|title=Venezia 61 - Out of competition|work=[[威尼斯雙年展|La Biennale di Venezia]]|accessdate=2021-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040822092839/http://www.labiennale.org/en/cinema/61miac/line-up/out-of-competition.html|archive-date=2004-08-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

[[DVD|DVD]]2004年12月14日在美國發售<ref name="DVDReleaseDate">{{cite web|url=https://www.dvdsreleasedates.com/movies/537/Collateral-(2004).html|title=Collateral (2004)|work=DVD Release Date|accessdate=2021-07-13|archive-date=2021-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228013234/https://www.dvdsreleasedates.com/movies/537/Collateral-(2004).html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[藍光光碟|藍光]]發售於2012年9月14日<ref name="Blu-ray.com-1">{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Collateral-Blu-ray/135438/|title=Collateral Blu-ray|work=Blu-ray.com|date=2012-09-14|accessdate=2021-07-13|archive-date=2016-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160217220303/http://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Collateral-Blu-ray/135438/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《落日殺神》連同《[[霹靂男兒|霹靂男兒]]》（1990年）、《[[黑色豪門企業|黑色豪門企業]]》（1993年）收錄於2013年10月15日推出的「湯姆·克魯斯三套電影版」（{{lang|en|Tom Cruise Triple Feature}}）藍光包中<ref name="Blu-ray.com-2">{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Tom-Cruise-Triple-Feature-Blu-ray/77607/|title=Tom Cruise Triple Feature Blu-ray|work=Blu-ray.com|date=2013-10-15|accessdate=2021-07-13|archive-date=2018-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180908144031/http://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Tom-Cruise-Triple-Feature-Blu-ray/77607/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年12月8日發售[[4K解析度|4K高畫質]]、藍光和數位版組合包<ref name="HDReport(2020-09-28)" /><ref name="Blu-ray.com-3">{{cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Collateral-4K-Blu-ray/277928/|title=Collateral 4K Blu-ray|work=Blu-ray.com|date=2020-12-08|accessdate=2021-07-13|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211200006/https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Collateral-4K-Blu-ray/277928/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 反響 ==
=== 票房 ===
在美國和加拿大，《落日殺神》首週從3188間戲院中收穫2470萬美元，擊敗《[[陰森林|陰森林]]》（1650萬美元），位居當週票房冠軍<ref name="MTV(2004-08-09)">{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1490030/collateral-kills-off-the-village-at-box-office/|title='COLLATERAL' KILLS OFF 'THE VILLAGE' AT BOX OFFICE|last=Rashbaum|first=Alyssa|work=MTV|date=2004-08-09|accessdate=2021-07-14|archive-date=2018-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005055750/http://www.mtv.com/news/1490030/collateral-kills-off-the-village-at-box-office/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="MovieWeb(2004-08-09)">{{cite news|url=https://movieweb.com/collateral-claims-the-top-spot-at-the-box-office/|title=Collateral claims the top spot at the box office|last=B.|first=Brian|work=MovieWeb|date=2004-08-09|accessdate=2021-07-14|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118044256/https://movieweb.com/collateral-claims-the-top-spot-at-the-box-office/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影共在戲院上映14週，美加票房總計1.01億美元，在2004年夏季檔期票房排名第12位<ref name="BOG(2004-09-17)">{{cite web|url=http://www.boxofficeguru.com/summer04.htm|title=Summer 2004|work=Box Office Guru|date=2004-09-17|accessdate=2021-07-14|archive-date=2020-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200120092458/http://www.boxofficeguru.com/summer04.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。本土票房加上國際市場的1.19億美元，全球票房收穫達2.2億美元；對比6500萬美元的預算，可謂成功。<ref name="BOM" />

=== 評價 ===
[[File:Jamie_Foxx_by_Gage_Skidmore.jpg|thumb]]的表演好評如潮，並為此入圍[[奧斯卡最佳男配角獎|奧斯卡最佳男配角獎]]]]
《落日殺神》在影評界和觀眾間獲得普遍好評。評論匯總網站[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據237條評論，本片獲得86%的新鮮度，均分7.50／10；共識評論：「在麥可·曼恩的招牌視覺效果和湯姆·克魯斯精實的反派表演的加持下，《落日殺神》是部時尚且令人信服的黑色驚悚片。」<ref name="RT">{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/collateral|title=Collateral (2004)|work=[[爛番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=Fandango Media|accessdate=2021-07-14|archive-date=2020-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200605045704/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/collateral|dead-url=no}}</ref>在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]網站上根據41條評論，獲得71分，屬「好壞參半的評價」<ref name="Metacritic">{{cite web|url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/collateral|title=Collateral Reviews|work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|publisher=[[CBS互動|CBS Interactive]]|accessdate=2021-07-14|archive-date=2021-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210709200040/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/collateral|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

克魯斯和福克斯的演技獲得影評肯定居多。《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》的{{le|史蒂芬·亨特|Stephen Hunter}}給予兩位演員的表演好評，並將該片概括為「類型片的最佳製作：循規蹈矩、遵守傳統且既熟悉又新鮮。」<ref name="WashingtonPost_Review-1">{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/articles/A44231-2004Aug5.html|title='Collateral': The Meter Keeps Running|last=Hunter|first=Stephen|work=[[華盛頓郵報|The Washington Post]]|date=2004-08-06|accessdate=2021-07-14|archive-date=2020-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200107140952/https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/articles/A44231-2004Aug5.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>知名影評人[[羅傑·埃伯特|羅傑·埃伯特]]從滿分4星中對電影給出3星半的高評，他稱讚了兩位演員，稱福克斯的演技是「意外的發現」<ref name="RogerEbert_Review">{{cite web|url=https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/collateral-2004|title='Collateral' a genre thriller, but so much more|last=Ebert|first=Roger|work=RogerEbert.com|date=2004-08-06|accessdate=2021-07-14|archive-date=2014-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141221180445/http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/collateral-2004|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[旧金山纪事报|旧金山纪事报]]》的{{le|米克·拉塞爾|Mick LaSalle}}除了稱讚克魯斯、蘋姬·史密斯、魯法洛和巴登外，還評論了福克斯的表演：「福克斯能演出符合角色傳達恐懼、困惑和沮喪的要求，但更重要的是，當某人深陷恐懼許久，容易變得又累又莽。」<ref name="SanFranciscoChronicle">{{cite web|url=https://www.sfgate.com/movies/article/The-hits-keep-on-coming-as-Cruise-Foxx-take-2735766.php|title=The hits keep on coming as Cruise, Foxx take harrowing cab ride around L.A.|last=LaSalle|first=Mick|work=[[旧金山纪事报|San Francisco Chronicle]]|date=2004-08-06|accessdate=2021-07-14|archive-date=2017-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171113232858/http://www.sfgate.com/movies/article/The-hits-keep-on-coming-as-Cruise-Foxx-take-2735766.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>《華盛頓郵報》的另一名影評人{{le|德森·湯姆森|Desson Thomson}}對福克斯給予了類似的讚揚，察覺這位演員「悄悄從隻手遮天的克魯斯中脫穎而出」<ref name="WashingtonPost_Review-2">{{cite web|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2004/08/06/AR2005033112621.html|title='Collateral': Foxx Grabs Wheel of Cruise Vehicle|last=Thomson|first=Desson|work=The Washington Post|date=2004-08-06|accessdate=2021-07-14|archive-date=2017-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171129213321/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2004/08/06/AR2005033112621.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。反之，《{{le|沙龍網|Salon.com|沙龍}}》雜誌的{{le|史蒂芬妮·梅耶|Stephanie Zacharek}}批評克魯斯的表現：「克魯斯的氣場既僵硬又虛假」，反之稱讚福克斯「非常舒適地融入他的角色，以至於讓文森關於艱難寫實世界的胡言亂語顯得毫無意義。但電影需要很長時間才能得出一項結論，這項結論從一開始就對任何理解力好的觀眾而言淺顯意見——活在現實世界的麥克斯才是電影的重點。」<ref name="Salon_Review">{{cite web|url=https://www.salon.com/2004/08/06/collateral/|title="Collateral"|last=Zacharek|first=Stephanie|work={{le|沙龍網|Salon.com|Salon}}|date=2004-08-06|accessdate=2021-07-14|archive-date=2012-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120706135622/http://www.salon.com/2004/08/06/collateral/|dead-url=no}}</ref>《{{le|星期日標準報|Evening Standard|倫敦星期日標準報}}》的[[威爾·塞爾夫|威爾·塞爾夫]]也有類似的想法，他稱讚福克斯從軟弱和搖擺不定到堅定與決心的轉變，但批評克魯斯缺乏讓文森活起來的深度邪惡<ref name="LondonEveningStandard_Review">{{cite web|url=https://www.standard.co.uk/culture/film/tom-s-too-good-7382273.html|title=Tom's too good|last=Self|first=Will|work={{le|星期日標準報|Evening Standard|London Evening Standard}}|date=2004-09-15|accessdate=2021-07-14|archive-date=2021-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210714100146/https://www.standard.co.uk/culture/film/tom-s-too-good-7382273.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在褒貶不一的評論中，《[[新闻周刊|新闻周刊]]》的{{le|大衛·安森|David Ansen}}讚賞該片，但批評電影的第三幕「籠統又牽強」<ref name="Newsweek_Review">{{cite web|url=https://www.newsweek.com/snap-judgement-movies-126329|title=SNAP JUDGEMENT: MOVIES|last=Ansen|first=David|work=[[新闻周刊|Newsweek]]|date=2004-08-08|accessdate=2021-07-14|archive-date=2019-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190322054152/https://www.newsweek.com/snap-judgement-movies-126329|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[時代雜誌|時代]]》雜誌的{{le|李察·希克爾|Richard Schickel}}除了曼恩的導演和比提的劇本外，還稱讚了演員們的演出。但他發現情節邏輯上不一致，加上「沒有足夠完全令人注目的事件來支撐這漫長的時長」<ref name="Time_Review">{{cite web|url=http://content.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,674780,00.html|title=The Hit Man Took a Taxi|last=Schickel|first=Richard|work=[[時代雜誌|Time]]|date=2004-08-01|accessdate=2021-07-14|archive-date=2017-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170727103237/http://content.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,674780,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[奧斯汀紀事|奧斯汀紀事]]》的瑪麗特·英曼（{{lang|en|Marrit Ingman}}）對曼恩的製作才華給予正面評價，但表示：「儘管情節旨在充實角色而偏離了幾場尷尬的戲，但在整體風格下並沒有太多的實質內容。」<ref name="AustinChronicle_Review">{{cite web|url=https://www.austinchronicle.com/events/film/2004-08-06/collateral/|title=Collateral|last=Ingman|first=Marrit|work=[[奧斯汀紀事|The Austin Chronicle]]|date=2004-08-06|accessdate=2021-07-14|archive-date=2020-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200915065250/https://www.austinchronicle.com/events/film/2004-08-06/collateral/|dead-url=no}}</ref>《{{le|板巖 (雜誌)|Slate (magazine)|板巖}}》雜誌的{{le|大衛·艾德爾斯坦|David Edelstein}}強調福克斯的表演「極佳」，並對電影的第一幕很滿意，但嘲笑了其餘部分：「《落日殺神》成了一連串招搖、混亂、過火的動作片，[[存在主義|存在主義者]]曼恩在當中證明了他差勁的動作戲，整個中段太糟糕了。」艾德爾斯坦還批評克魯斯的表演像個「機器人」<ref name="Slate_Review">{{cite web|url=https://slate.com/culture/2004/08/collateral-s-taxicab-philosopher.html|title=Taxicab Confessions|last=Edelstein|first=David|work={{le|板巖 (雜誌)|Slate (magazine)|Slate}}|date=2004-08-05|accessdate=2021-07-14|archive-date=2020-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200915065300/https://slate.com/culture/2004/08/collateral-s-taxicab-philosopher.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[世界社會主義網站|世界社會主義網站]]的大衛·華許（{{lang|en|David Walsh}}）不喜歡這部電影，除了批評了片中許多的不合理之處（如文森的瘋狂殺手作風、證人非得在同一晚被殺死等）外，還認為曼恩常被讚賞的「時尚」僅用於炫耀，根本言之無物；他在評論中寫道：「該片整體上缺乏緊迫和具體感，也沒有對美國現今領先地位者所過的特殊生活有任何明確的認知。」<ref name="WSWS_Review">{{cite web|url=https://www.wsws.org/en/articles/2004/08/coll-a27.html|title=Small oases and the much larger desert|last=Walsh|first=David|work=[[世界社會主義網站|World Socialist Web Site]]|date=2004-08-27|accessdate=2021-07-14|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125110450/https://www6.wsws.org/en/articles/2004/08/coll-a27.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

《時代》雜誌<ref name="Time(2004-12-17)">{{cite web|url=http://content.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,1999700_1998807_1998865,00.html|title=Top 10 Everything 2004|last=Schickel|first=Richard|work=Time|date=2004-12-17|accessdate=2021-07-14|archive-date=2014-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715094216/http://content.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,1999700_1998807_1998865,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、影評人{{le|李察·洛普|Richard Roeper}}<ref name="InnerMind">{{cite web|url=https://www.innermind.com/misc/e_r_top.htm|title=EBERT AND ROEPER TOP TEN LISTS|work=InnerMind|accessdate=2021-07-14|archive-date=2018-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180525184730/http://www.innermind.com/misc/e_r_top.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[美國電影學會|美國電影學會]] <ref name="AFI">{{cite web|url=https://www.afi.com/award/afi-awards-2004/|title=AFI Awards 2004|work=[[美國電影學會|American Film Institute]]|accessdate=2021-07-14|archive-date=2020-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200619154938/https://www.afi.com/award/afi-awards-2004/|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[國家評論協會|國家評論協會]]<ref name="NationalBoardofReview">{{cite web|url=http://www.nbrmp.org/awards/past.cfm?year=2004|title=National Board of Review of Motion Pictures - Awards|work=[[國家評論協會|National Board of Review Awards 2004]]|accessdate=2021-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100813145503/http://www.nbrmp.org/awards/past.cfm?year=2004|archive-date=2010-08-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>將《落日殺神》列入年度十佳片單中。2008年，《[[洛杉磯時報|洛杉磯時報]]》的一組撰稿和編輯評選過去25年來的25部最佳洛杉磯電影{{notetag|名單的兩項標準：電影必須傳達一些關於洛杉磯經歷的內在真相，只允許每位導演的一部片入選。}}，《落日殺神》因「對洛杉磯的處理充滿力量和魅力」而位居第九名<ref name="LATimes(2008-08-31)">{{cite web|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2008/aug/31/entertainment/ca-25films31|title=L.A.’s story is complicated, but they got it|last=Boucher|first=Geoff|work=[[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]]|date=2008-08-31|accessdate=2021-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081108175122/http://articles.latimes.com/2008/aug/31/entertainment/ca-25films31|archive-date=2008-11-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。《[[廣播時報|廣播時報]]》2018年將《落日殺神》評為克魯斯十大佳片榜中的第七位<ref name="RadioTimes(2018-08-31)">{{cite news|url=https://www.radiotimes.com/movies/top-10-tom-cruise-films/|title=Top 10 Tom Cruise movies of all time|last=Folley|first=Tom|work=[[廣播時報|Radio Times]]|date=2018-08-31|accessdate=2021-07-14|archive-date=2021-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210714100213/https://www.radiotimes.com/movies/top-10-tom-cruise-films/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2021年，[[Screen_Rant|Screen Rant]]網站評選「麥可·曼恩電影中十大難忘角色」名單中將克魯斯飾演的文森排於第七名<ref name="ScreenRant(2021-06-28)">{{cite news|url=https://screenrant.com/the-most-memorable-characters-from-michael-mann-movies/|title=The 10 Most Memorable Characters From Michael Mann Movies|last=Sherlock|first=Ben|work=[[Screen_Rant|Screen Rant]]|date=2021-06-28|accessdate=2021-07-14|archive-date=2021-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210711184705/https://screenrant.com/the-most-memorable-characters-from-michael-mann-movies/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

